# HTML intructions

- Use modern HTML 5 whenever generating code.
- Remember that this is a Hugo blog, so HTML should be compatible with it. Hugo
  uses the Go's html/template package when rendering HTML files.
- Target modern Web browsers and phones (iPhones, Pixel phones).
- Avoid pulling external dependencies and scripts, if possible. Prefer simple
  static website with minimal dependencies and no bloat.